race.comment: ALNAHEL (11) First up from a 93 week break. In the money when 2nd last time here but will be down in distance. Worth consideration. TRANSFERRED (2) Placed 2nd last start at the track and hard to fault at the distance. Jockey Muhammad Aldaham and trainer Thamer Aldaihani can't be overlooked. Well placed and has solid claims. SNAFIYA (4) Was ordinary when 7th last run at Taif and bit of extra work to do with more weight. Should be going forward early. Exhibiting good form this campaign. Expect to go close. MSAYEH (1) Narrowly clinched the victory last time around here and proven performer at this trip. Will be pushing for a forward position early. Been in the money each start this preparation. Can get the job done.
